title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Afters with Danny Lomas
description:
On our new weekly lightning round mini ep with Danny Lomas, we’re fucking around with London, UK slang, funeral fits, Liam Gallagher, Harry Styles, all time Brit style, Boris Johnson, the Queen, drunk munchies and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
